8. Model module
---------------
The normalisation values of light and phase curves shall not exceed values of 1
but due to rounding problems when reading the FITS file it can happen that
slightly larger value occur. To circumvent the issue a small margin of 1e-8 has
been added to the maximum value of 1, well below the required precision for
flux normalisations (#2149).


9. Numerics module
------------------
None


10. Observation module
----------------------
None


11. Optimization module
-----------------------
None


12. Sky module
--------------
The GSkyDir class now signals that ra/dec or l/b are cached when they were
computed in the gal2equ() and equ2gal() methods, improving hence the speed
of the clients (#2148).


