20. CTA interface
-----------------
The GCTAPsfKing::r_max() method returned an infinite radius for a too small
gamma parameter. If the gamma parameter is too small the method now returns
a maximum radius of zero, and the GCTAPsfKing::update() method will set the
normalization to zero (#2133).


